8791,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T11:58:01.000Z","msg":"以前覺得人生好灰暗 知道左一個消息 我開始感恩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e37622c01b986e4b15ff5422fb7fc350b5ee42db","tid":1698791,"uid":204265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4fa47ea374ef6bc497eb4333e67a72717ab9543","tid":1698791,"uid":277036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"496a89d62065163700d5bcb80db5bed644fdb59a","tid":1698791,"uid":204265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f36288be1f0c791c20219221bf3570229c0dc6f","tid":1698791,"uid":260796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T18:05:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T18:07:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T09:05:45.000Z","msg":"我呀爸本身都諗住唔要我<br />\n我都有諗過同樣問題 最親既人都想自己死<br />\n但我呀爸死左之後 我都係有傷心難過<br />\n配唔配生存 唔應該由其他人定義既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T13:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c7d118e156bcc5ffe05c2d0229a9b7acfbf3a7","tid":1698791,"uid":194628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T13:34:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a83a03575c81f889c85cbeca9a6c0e5ec776b0b4","tid":1698791,"uid":113107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22c7d118e156bcc5ffe05c2d0229a9b7acfbf3a7","tid":1698791,"uid":194628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T13:34:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T08:37:47.000Z","msg":"我本身細佬都差啲出唔到世 老母話想落佢個時<br />\n佢係個肚到係咁踢 好似好唔想走咁 所以唔忍心最後無到<br />\n有時望住細佬 覺得生命都幾有趣 活生生嘅人可能會從未存在過 <br />\n有機會睇下問米個啲問下你呀爺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a39b998c0aed6996c0b709d5a55c4f508221637e","tid":1698791,"uid":113107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4fa47ea374ef6bc497eb4333e67a72717ab9543","tid":1698791,"uid":277036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"496a89d62065163700d5bcb80db5bed644fdb59a","tid":1698791,"uid":204265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f36288be1f0c791c20219221bf3570229c0dc6f","tid":1698791,"uid":260796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T18:05:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T18:07:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T09:05:45.000Z","msg":"我呀爸本身都諗住唔要我<br />\n我都有諗過同樣問題 最親既人都想自己死<br />\n但我呀爸死左之後 我都係有傷心難過<br />\n配唔配生存 唔應該由其他人定義既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T08:39:11.000Z","msg":"講得岩 唔通呢個世界咁多人想你死<br />\n你又要一一為佢地嘅諗法而唔開心咩<br />\n錯嘅唔係你 只係咁岩唔想要一條生命 唔想負責任個個係你親人"},{"pid":"27612cfceeea74d1c663ff3938fe0c2b8fd212fd","tid":1698791,"uid":288086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T10:11:25.000Z","msg":"我感恩我有存在過<br />\n但只想不用活太久<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}